gomodel:SYNGO_2127  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig.1: \"TBS produced a slightly more protracted increase in activated pPyk2 colocalized with PSD-95 (Fig. 1C).\". Experimental description: \"Acute transverse hippocampal slices (350 μm) were prepared from young adult (30- to 60-d-old) male Sprague Dawley rats using a Leica Vibroslicer (VT 1000S) or McIlwain tissue chopper, as described previously (Kramár et al., 2002, 2006; Chen et al., 2007).\"" ;
